  "lore": "The Night Raptors are less a martial elite than a bloody coterie of murderers joined by similar proclivities and chosen styles of warfare. The Night Raptors find bleak joy in soaring above the battlefield like screaming predators bunting for victims and savour most that stark moment of clarity when a victim witnesses their death reflected back to them in the eyes of their killer. In battle they emerge adorned in grisly trophies and draped in flayed human skin, their intent to strike abject fear into the hearts of their enemies.",
